name: <iter::adapters::fuse::Fuse<I> as iter::traits::double_ended::DoubleEndedIterator>::try_rfold
src:
fn try_rfold<Acc, Fold, R>(&mut self, acc: Acc, fold: Fold) -> R
    where
        Self: Sized,
        Fold: FnMut(Acc, Self::Item) -> R,
        R: Try<Output = Acc>,
    {
        FuseImpl::try_rfold(self, acc, fold)
    }
